Name: ISEKAI QUEST
About the game: You were summoned to Harem World, full of Anime Girls. You can seduce any girls you want to, but it comes at a price. Can you complete the quest and save the world? Welcome to the Isekai, the world of anime girls! Isekai Quest! is a Moe Puzzle RPG Game, Enhances tactics and fun by combining a 3-match puzzle with rogue-lite. Isekai Quest! provides a lifelike and immersive experience by achieving realistic interactions with cute anime characters.
